- JavaScript enabled
- Internet connection for AI processing
- 2MB available bandwidth for initial load

### A.2 API Requirements
- Google Gemini API access with sufficient quota
- Rate limiting compliance (varies by API tier)
- HTTPS certificate for secure communications

### A.3 Deployment Requirements
- Static web hosting capability
- CDN integration for global performance
- SSL/TLS certificate for security compliance

